AMD Products Group Head Departs; CEO to Serve as Interim Head

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-09-22T20:43:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/amd-products-group-head-departs-ceo-to-serve-as-interim-head.html
Advanced Micro Devices Inc. (AMD)  said
Products Group General Manager Rick Bergman is leaving and Chief
Executive Officer Rory Read will serve as interim general
manager.  AMD also said that Paul Struhsaker joined the company
to lead a new commercial business division.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  